# Google Cloud Platform (GCP) Commands and Key Topics for a GCP Engineer/Consultant

This repository contains essential commands and concepts for working with Google Cloud Platform (GCP) as a GCP Engineer/Consultant. The guide includes common operations for Compute Engine, Kubernetes Engine (GKE), Networking, IAM, and more. This documentation can be useful for both beginners and experienced engineers.

